  },
  {
   "hash": "7a0e5c3991acb5d6",
   "zh": "\"What art reapers remnants of?\" (答案: anci / ench / fore)",
   "note": "[二輪 reviewer 修]"
  },
  {
   "hash": "32cb04275ea81d34",
